":1459323,"uid":132352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:06:12.000Z","msg":"好多謝地鐵手足  但真係停一停  諗一諗帶到出來既效果"},{"pid":"a401e316a4e624599407b8afbac75358a1831d64","tid":1459323,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:06:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">塞機場好過塞鐵<br />\n成效和對政府壓力更大<br />\n<br />\n最低收入的一群真的手停口停，佢哋真係唔返工唔得，你咁搞你叫佢哋點支持/同意你？<br />\n<br />\n普羅民意 很重要， 我哋嘅敵人唔係普羅大眾 而係政府， 點解要 減少自己嘅支持者而增加自己嘅敵人呢？<br />\n<br />\n除非你係鬼啦！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"303928dbce085a7ae6d0290a30b333f0e7112b5e","tid":1459323,"uid":132352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:07:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa9c568da3486e8fd7a6bc1d32c8d3de18442af3","tid":1459323,"uid":49756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25b14d42a4a23e2ba21594f82c452117825ccedc","tid":1459323,"uid":190285,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:04:24.000Z","msg":"希望各位塞鐵手足三思<br />\n<br />\n85配合大型活動做係好，但平日就不了<br />\n<br />\n不過你地做左都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:07:38.000Z","msg":"唔好講唔割 你咁樣就比佢地道德綁架咗 <br />\n你要諗割唔割嘅 係先諗究竟佢地咁做係唔係真係啱<br />\n如果佢地本身一開始就唔聽人講咁衝去做<br />\n點解大家仲要盲目咁去支持一件明知大家都唔支持嘅野？<br />\n咁你所講嘅唔割有冇經過自己嘅思考 定係盲目跟從「不分化」嘅大方向呢？"},{"pid":"b3a819069d7d6667bd8daf0e7d9296047952ebc5","tid":1459323,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"[輸出革命］由今日起，不叫港獨，改叫「廣獨」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1447204\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1447204</a><br />\n幫手支持廣獨，將革命思想傳入中國！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7nZFbOE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7nZFbOE.png&h=4fd8318f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n巴打可以用下面條link去印，set左a5 size<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1qG8N4AsnroP--EywjjvB